{"word":"G5242 - ὑπερέχω - hyperéchō - hoop-er-ekh'-o - Better","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπερέχω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hyperéchō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-er-ekh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Better</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மேலாயிரு, மேன்மையாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"1. to have or hold over one"},{"paragraph":"2. to stand out, rise above, overtop"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5228 - ὑπέρ - hypér - hoop-er'/5228\">G5228</a> and <a href=\"#/G2192 - ἔχω - échō - ekh'-o/2192\">G2192</a>; to <i>hold</i> oneself <i>above</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>excel</i>; participle (as adjective, or neuter as noun) <i>superior</i>, <i>superiority:</i> - better, excellency, higher, pass, supreme.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5242/5242\">G5242</a>, <a href=\"#/G5247/5247\">G5247</a>"}]}